Class Dimensions

java.lang.Object
  org.lsmp.djep.vectorJep.Dimensions

public class Dimensions
extends java.lang.Object

A class to represent a set of dimensions. Might be 1 for 0-dimensional numbers. [3] for a 3D vector [3,3] for a matrix
